Noto Emoji (raster pack)
========================

When you populate ``png/`` and ``manifest.json`` using
``scripts/vendor_noto_emoji.py`` from a clone of the upstream repository, those
image files come from the Noto Emoji project:

  https://github.com/googlefonts/noto-emoji

See the LICENSE and README in that repository for image and tooling licenses
(Apache License 2.0 applies to most image resources and build tools there).

Until you run the vendor script, this directory ships with an empty manifest so
the app falls back to Unicode glyphs in the emoji picker.
